data.description: Tree lined streets await you. Great schools. Great parks. Lots of shopping. As you enter this home you immediately notice the care and detail given to every element inside and out. Home has been kept at an immaculate level. Professional grade. Large tiled entry way with spectacular view of open floor plan. HIGHLY SOUGHT AFTER DOWNSTAIRS BEDROOM & TWO BATHROOMS! Breathtaking entertainers kitchen with center island. Living Room with surround sound and grand fireplace overlooks the fantastic backyard. 6 Large bedrooms with walk in closets, upgraded bathrooms include private, guest and jack & Jill. Outside is complete with large space for potential RV parking, patio spaces and grassy area for all kinds of family fun and adventures. Must see. Will not last long.
